title: The FoodSaver® FM1510 Fresh Food Preservation System -  Space Saving
description: The FoodSaver Fresh Food Preservation System seals in freshness of foods stored in the fridge, pantry and on the go. Easily and conveniently vacuum seal FoodSaver Fresh Containers and Vacuum Zipper Bags for storage of everyday foods, leftovers and prep-ahead ingredients. Its compact design is made for everyday countertop use and its one-touch sealing allows for hand-free operation once the sealing process starts.

transcripts: Not only does my food saver fresh food preservation system save food it also saves on space. Its compact design barely takes up any room on my counter. The zipper bags and stackable containers make food storage easy and the nestable design let me store a variety of containers. Trust your food freshness to the new FoodSaver fresh food preservation system.
